 "1/united states/north carolina/", "2/united states/north carolina/watauga/", "3/united states/north carolina/watauga/boone/"], "contributor": ["university of north carolina at chapel hill library, chapel hill, nc"], "date": "1930-10-23", "dates": ["1930-10-23"], "description": ["OCTOBER 23 1930 LeesMc\u00dfae Installs New Student Council Installation service for the offi cers of the Student Council of Lees Mc\u00dfae College was held Monday Oc tober 13 Rev W R Smith director of religious activities conducted the service After making a brief talk Mr Smith charged Mr Zimmerman as faculty advisor of the council who then charged he members of the council The council is composed of the following students President George Baker first vicepresident C L Stucky second vicepresident Rob ert Hoss secretary Edith Robbins treasurer Lloyd Blalock president of the senior college class Otis Lon don president of junior college class Gailen Willis president of the sen ior high school class Mary Young president of the Junior High School class Robert Clothier president of the sophomore class Jincy Winegar president of the freshman high school class Sam Lankford senior college class representative Kitty Guilfiams and Margaret Mozingo ju nior college class representatives Frances Morris and day student rep resentative Clyde Cooke After the ceremony of installation the student body rose and with up lifted hand pledged itself by an oath of allegiance to uphold the council in all things and to abide by its rul ings The"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-12T17:31:08.455Z", "group": ["ndnp/ncu", "university-of-north-carolina-chapel-hill-library-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82007642/1930-10-23/ed-1/?sp=3", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ncu:batch_ncu_appling_ver02:data:sn82007642:00279558194:1930102301:0763/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=421&w=290", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service